groups/160692051006024/permalink/616602775414947?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F160692051006024%2Fpermalink%2F616602775414947%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=153f6f97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/160692051006024/permalink/616602775414947?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"e4bbd0e60d2cfedb0a3239599755549040cdf383","tid":1255951,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ff1551f7fa64f7f546d633fa18a2db82e4cbb8","tid":1255951,"uid":233325,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:02:01.000Z","msg":"大家不能不承認風向改變左，<br />\n但係你唔可以只係到埋怨香港人善忘，<br />\n亦唔可以單單只指責對方輿論戰，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>更加唔可以怪責戰友！</strong></span></span><br />\n問題在於，我地無左明確目的。<br />\n係你嘅社交媒體呢幾日幾時出現過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>四大訴求</strong></span></span>？<br />\n係連登啲post有幾多重申過？<br />\n大家盲目地去追擊黑警、高官、護士、導演明星時，有無諗過人地已經唔記得左你地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>係為咩而抗爭緊</strong></span>？<br />\n我明白如果分裂到人地陣營大家都會好興奮，如果國際有更多關注又會畀更大嘅支持大家！<br />\n不過，做野分緩急輕重，希望大家做住各種文宣工作時，可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加多啲力宣傳同策劃626行動</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n你<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>宣傳越不足，只會越少人出現</strong></span></span>，出現嘅人又會心灰意冷，再黎就係當下次再有集會，又再少啲人出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住唔好<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>俾人模糊焦點，唔好俾人分化，團結係最大籌碼</strong></span></span>，香港人，記住不撤不散！<br />\n<br />\n請緊記，人數係最大優勢，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有人唔一定贏，但係無人就一定輸硬！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzSwrWT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzSwrWT.png&h=5afd0388&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ON87KJA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FON87KJA.png&h=a3c0cb02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9feaf9f7c8fcf82d55542e69ebd91719fe639f61","tid":1255951,"uid":11827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:04:47.000Z","msg":"唔得閒攞出嚟打下J谷爆咗點算 大佬一個月都未過咁快唔想人講 你試下係其它地方揾 200萬+1人出嚟都難呀 真係無乜可能"},{"pid":"28224cb90345b6ccd4a5d731f5560e0ff060ee05","tid":1255951,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9feaf9f7c8fcf82d55542e69ebd91719fe639f61","tid":1255951,"uid":11827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:04:47.000Z","msg":"唔得閒攞出嚟打下J谷爆咗點算 大佬一個月都未過咁快唔想人講 你試下係其它地方揾 200萬+1人出嚟都難呀 真係無乜可能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:07:25.000Z","msg":"咁又點呀<br />\n 代表你咩都做得？"},{"pid":"bab897c94355e91eba0d6f34dd727901aef35a8c","tid":1255951,"uid":200274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"爸爸媽媽 我哋有啲嘢想講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dauArS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dauArS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d13b6640eea3ad47888c110eb3a5f1092b05452f","tid":1255951,"uid":11827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28224cb90345b6ccd4a5d731f5560e0ff060ee05","tid":1255951,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9feaf9f7c8fcf82d55542e69ebd91719fe639f61","tid":1255951,"uid":11827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:04:47.000Z","msg":"唔得閒攞出嚟打下J谷爆咗點算 大佬一個月都未過咁快唔想人講 你試下係其它地方揾 200萬+1人出嚟都難呀 真係無乜可能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:07:25.000Z","msg":"咁又點呀<br />\n 代表你咩都做得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:09:15.000Z","msg":"你呢句 代表咩都做得 好有問題 咁你覺得佢地又做咗咩唔做得嘅事出嚟"}]}